  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4  \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The coconut plucked by the father became the son",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An incident occurred in Namunukula area where a father was plucking a coconut from a coconut tree and fell on his son's head.",
        "It has also been revealed that the deceased was a 10th standard student from Namunukala-Miyanakandura area.",
        "The day before yesterday (29) around 6.30 pm, while the father was picking coconuts by climbing a 50 feet high coconut tree, the coconut fell on the son's head when he came out of the house.",
        "After this, the son died early today while being taken to Badula Hospital for treatment.",
        "At the same time, the police said that they will take legal action against the 55-year-old father, who caused the death, on the charge of carelessly plucking coconuts."
      ],
